General Information

Delicious dark chocolate with mint crisps that's gluten free, low carb, keto friendly and has no sugar added so you can enjoy all the pleasure without the gain!

Warnings

Contains soy.
Despite our best cleaning efforts, this product may contain traces of milk, peanuts, and/or tree nuts because it shares equipment with other products.
Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.

Ingredients

No Sugar Added Dark Chocolate (93%) [Cocoa Solids, Polydextrose, Natural Sweetener (Erythritol), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour, Natural Sweetener (Steviol Glycosides)], Sugar Free Peppermint Chips (6%) (Isomalt, Water, Natural Peppermint Flavour), Natural Flavour.
No sugar added dark chocolate contains 70% cocoa solids min.
Contains Soy.
